General.Name: Wyld Networks AB
General.Description: Wyld Networks AB (publ), together with its subsidiaries, operates as a virtual satellite network operator that develops and delivers wireless technology solutions in Sweden and internationally. It offers Wyld Connect and Wyld Fusion that provides end-to-end hybrid satellite and terrestrial Internet of Things (IoT) connectivity solutions for customers to collect data. The company's solution enables terrestrial and satellite connectivity for IoT devices and sensors. It also offers mesh networks that utilize location aware technology and wirelessly mesh devices to enhance customer experience. The company was founded in 2021 and is based in Malmö, Sweden.
